    pc "Eh..."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:22
translate spanish mills2_63029bd2:

    # bs "But since he's gone for the week, I haven't been able to get any and I'm feeling a little pent up, you know?"
    bs "Pero como se ha ido toda la semana, no he podido tener nada y me siento un poco reprimida, ¿sabes?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:24
translate spanish mills2_0110cdb8:

    # bs "I'm just craving it."
    bs "Simplemente lo estoy deseando."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:30
translate spanish mills2_c793b45c:

    # bs "Right. You're right. I'm sorry."
    bs "Claro. Tienes razón. Lo siento."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:31
translate spanish mills2_a346dca8:

    # bs "I won't bring it up again. Back to work [pcname]."
    bs "No volveré a sacar el tema. Volvamos al trabajo [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:33
translate spanish mills2_09914973:

    # "I go back to what I had been doing and Mrs. Mills goes back to working at her desk. We don't talk any more the rest of the day."
    "Vuelvo a lo que estaba haciendo y la Sra. Mills vuelve a trabajar en su escritorio. No volvemos a hablar en todo el resto del día."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:36
translate spanish mills2_5e9ea2bc:

    # "I drive home, thinking that I could have maybe done something with Mrs. Mills, but it hadn't felt right."
    "Conduzco de vuelta a casa, pensando que quizá podría haber hecho algo con la Sra. Mills, pero no me parecía bien."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:37
translate spanish mills2_64e0e1c1:

    # "She is my boss and I don't want to get in any sort of relationship with her past that."
    "Es mi jefa y no quiero tener ningún tipo de relación con ella más allá de eso."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:43
translate spanish mills2_76f8dc88:

    # bs "Oh yeah?"
    bs "¿Ah, sí?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:44
translate spanish mills2_46f44fb2:

