    bs "¿Te gustaría eso?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:46
translate spanish mills2_d529cf63:

    # bs "I bet you would like that. You'd like being my little fuckboy?"
    bs "Apuesto a que te gustaría. ¿Te gustaría ser mi pequeño follador?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:47
translate spanish mills2_1ca45f42:

    # pc "Well, yeah."
    pc "Bueno, sí."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:48
translate spanish mills2_92bc68f0:

    # bs "I'd be lying if I said that I haven't thought about it."
    bs "Mentiría si dijera que no lo he pensado."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:50
translate spanish mills2_a81d699f:

    # bs "I am curious as to how you would be, since you're so young."
    bs "Tengo curiosidad por saber cómo serías, ya que eres tan joven."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:51
translate spanish mills2_262400a9:

    # bs "I've had younger lovers in the past, but none quite as young as you."
    bs "He tenido amantes más jóvenes en el pasado, pero ninguno tan joven como tú."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:52
translate spanish mills2_29cb0621:

    # bs "I bet you could fuck all night, couldn't you?"
    bs "Apuesto a que podrías follar toda la noche, ¿verdad?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:53
translate spanish mills2_f29db352:

    # pc "Sure. Any time."
    pc "Claro. Cuando quieras."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:55
translate spanish mills2_493e0d50:

    # bs "You are tempting, that is for sure."
    bs "Eres tentadora, eso es seguro."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:57
translate spanish mills2_289f1f92:

    # bs "But I'm your boss and we shouldn't complicate that relationship."
    bs "Pero soy tu jefa y no deberíamos complicar esa relación."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:58
translate spanish mills2_fefc9af5:

    # bs "If I wore you out by fucking you all the time, who would clean my office?"
    bs "Si te dejara exhausto follando contigo todo el tiempo, ¿quién limpiaría mi oficina?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:59
translate spanish mills2_56781dd8:

    # bs "I'll just wait for my personal trainer to get back from his vacation."
    bs "Esperaré a que mi entrenador personal vuelva de sus vacaciones."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:60
translate spanish mills2_e91981f0:

    # pc "Okay, Mrs. Mills, but you're missing out."
    pc "De acuerdo, Sra. Mills, pero se está perdiendo algo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:62
translate spanish mills2_0cd671b4:

    # "When I turn around to start cleaning, she slaps me on my ass hard."
