# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:65
translate spanish mills2_1da8b21d:

    # "I do as she said and go back to cleaning the office."
    "Hago lo que me dice y vuelvo a limpiar la oficina."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:66
translate spanish mills2_cbbe4d0e:

    # "The whole time, I am distracted by Mrs. Mills."
    "Todo el rato, estoy distraído pensando en la señora Mills."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:67
translate spanish mills2_7e488788:

